Tips on Scheduling Reports

Some tips to keep in mind about timings, limits, and email notifications when scheduling a report.

Scheduling Report Runs
You can’t create schedules for joined reports.
Your org can schedule up to 200 reports.
Scheduled reports run in the time zone of the user who set up the schedule.

Emailing Scheduled Reports
You can't email scheduled reports to Chatter Free users.
Emailed reports don’t include report charts.
Reports display only the first 2,000 records.
The maximum size for emailed reports is 10 MB.
